  "identifier": "HB 258",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to the transportation of milk.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 189.222 to allow vehicles with a gross weight of up to 90,000 pounds transporting fluid milk from a farm to the first market to operate on any state highway; allow for a 10% weight tolerance; provide exceptions and limitations; amend KRS 189.221 to conform.",
